{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeselectcomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeSelectComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of select","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"select"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSelect","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSelectComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"SelectComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"select"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Select"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllSelectComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06SelectB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for select component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomSelectComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the select component tokens you want.","","        override var selectSizeMaxHeightContainerIcon: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","","        override var selectColorBorderHover: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var selectSpaceColumnGap: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomSelectComponentTokensProvider: LinkComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomSelectComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(select: CustomSelectComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(select: CustomSelectComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let selectComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let selectComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(